title: Five Nights at Freddy's 4/FNAF 4 Nightmare Foxy Teaser and Hidden Details
tags: ["Five Nights At Freddy's", 'fnaf 4', 'fnaf 4 confirmed', 'fnaf 4 teaser', 'fnaf 4 foxy', 'fnaf4', "five nights at freddy's 4", "five nights at freddy's 4 foxy", 'fnaf 4 nightmare', 'fnaf teaser', 'fnaf theory', 'fnaf 4 theory', 'toridori', 'fnaf 4 rumours', "five nights at freddy's 4 confirmed", 'foxy the pirate', "five nights at freddy's 4 teaser", 'fnaf 4 animatronics', 'fnaf 4 scottgames', 'fnaf 4 scott cawthon']
description:
Scott Cawthon updated his website once again, giving us another horrifying first look at a FNAF 4 Nightmare animatronic - this time it's Foxy!

In this video I look closely at the details of the new Foxy the Pirate image and talk about what it could entail for the story of Five Nights at Freddy's 4.

There are a lot of hidden secrets in this image, such as the word 'NIGHTMARE' hidden in Foxy's teeth, the phrase 'OUT OF ORDER' at the bottom left, and the numbers 8 and 7 hidden in his right eye. 

All this definitely points to the Bite of '87, and I personally believe it labels Foxy as the culprit! I'd still love to know what you guys think about what I talked about and debate it in the comment section. 

I'm so pumped for this game now - can't believe there is still five months to go! I don't know if I'll actually have the guts to play though... hah.

title: Camping Lanterna Camp - Kroatien - Istrien - Porec
description:
http://www.selectcamp.de/Camping/Kroatien/Istrien/Selectcamp-Camping-Lanterna-Camp/1567

Lanterna Camp liegt nicht weit von der sonnenverwöhnten Stadt Poreç.
Auf diesem Campingplatz gibt es viel zu erleben: Wassergymnastik in einem der beiden Swimmingpools, faulenzen am Strand oder in der malerischen Bucht, die Kondition aufpeppen im Fitnessraum ...

Urlaub auf Camping Lanterna Camp bietet eröffnet Ihnen tolle Möglichkeiten! Genießen Sie die fantastische Natur und erkunden Sie die Umgebung, egal ob zu Fuß, mit dem Fahrrad oder mit dem Kanu.

Durch die super Lage direkt am Meer hat Camping Lanterna bekommen Sie die Wasserspaß-Garantie! Es gibt einen Süß- und einen Salzwasser-Swimmingpool (mit Hydromassage), einen Spielplatz, Fitnessmöglichkeiten, einen Tennisplatz, Aerobics, ... Wassersportler können surfen oder Kanu fahren.

Kulinarisch verwöhnt werden Sie auf dem Campingplatz im Restaurant oder in der Pizzeria. Lassen Sie den Abend in der Bar ausklingen. Wenn Sie endlich einmal wieder mit der ganzen Familie zusammen kochen wollen, dann finden Sie alles, was Sie brauchen, im Supermarkt auf Lanterna Camp. Und abends geht es dann in die Familien-Disco mit dem tollen Show-Programm! Am nächsten Tag wird eine Radtour nach Poreç gestartet. Der perfekte Familien-Urlaub!

title: The ship that saved two thousand Brits!
description:
As maritime naming ceremonies go, this was an unusual one given that most people in the UK are already familiar with this particular ship.  Celebrity Eclipse, the brand new cruise ship which made a dramatic dash to rescue 2,200 British holidaymakers from Spain this week, did so without ever having been officially named.  Today, that was finally put right when her Godmother, British yachtswoman and breast cancer survivor, Emma Pontin, undertook the highly coveted task of christening the ship by releasing a magnum of champagne to smash against the helm (Sat, 24th April).

Celebrity Eclipse was scheduled to arrive in the UK on Tuesday morning for a week of launch celebrations including a two-day maiden voyage in the waters off the South coast of the UK.  But rather than 500 specially-invited VIPs, her first official passengers turned out to be hundreds of weary tourists who had been stranded in Bilbao, Spain as a result of the volcanic ash cloud that was covering Northern Europe.  In honour of the ships inspirational Godmother, Hampshire-born Emma Pontin, whose brave fight against breast cancer saw her continuing to race, sail and instruct during her treatment, todays naming ceremony was timed to coincide a breast cancer charity fundraising event. Thousands of men, women and families donned decorated bras to take part in the 5km and 10km Celebrity Sunwalk around Southampton, reaching the finish line by the docks at Mayflower Park in time to join in the naming ceremony celebrations.  A performance from American R&B performer, Jocelyn Brown, provided entertainment for the crowds.

title: 색소폰연주 / 사랑의 기쁨
description:
사랑해, 또 사랑해, 그리고 사랑해...
 
사랑이 아름다운 건
이 세상에
산소 같은 미소가 있기 때문이야.
 
사랑하면
행복해지는 이유가 뭔 줄 아니?
 
너 때문에, 나 때문에
웃을 수 있고
나를 생각해 주는 한 사람이 있어
든든한 울타리 안에서
편안히 쉴 수 있기 때문이야.
 
사랑하면
외로워지는 이유를 알고 있니?
그건... 그건 말이야?
 
따뜻한 살갗이 그립고
숨소리가 그립고
꼭 안아 주고 싶고
키스해 주고 싶은데
곁에 없는 안타까움이
더 외롭게 하는 거야.
 
보고 싶다.
너를 만나면
목을 꼭 잡고 키스해 줄 거야.
사랑해, 또 사랑해, 그리고 사랑해...
 
- 옮기는 글 -

description:

Да, я читер и события, произошедшие в видео, были на специальном читерском сервере, где все играли с читами. Разве по названию не видно? Хватит писать очевидную чушь.
- Скинь ип.
Ребят, я бы с радостью, но этому видео более двух лет и я давно потерял айпи этого сервера. К тому же, как я помню, его перевели на новую ксс и он сразу же опустел. Скорее всего, он уже давным-давно не работает.

description:
Hawkeyes destroy Minnesota  31-13, with a  Homecoming victory. 


The Iowa Hawkeyes stormed out to a 24-0 halftime en route to handing Minnesota its first loss with a 31-13 Homecoming victory Saturday afternoon inside Kinnick Stadium. 

Home Sweet Home! The hawkeyes welcome the Flody of Rosedale trophy back where he belongs!!! 


Sophomore running back Mark Weisman had 177 yards -- 8.4 per attempt -- on 21 carries with a touchdown. Weisman has gone over the 100-yard mark in each of the last three games.

 Senior quarterback James Vandenberg completed 18-of-31 passes for 192 yards with a touchdown, while senior Keenan Davis had six catches for 50 yards.

"After one game, you're kind of like hmmm... hope I am seeing it right," said Ferentz of Weisman. "Then after two weeks, you start thinking, this guy might not be bad. 

After three games, a lot of us are starting to think maybe this guy is a running back. His fullback days may be numbered... he may be retiring from that spot."

title: Frontier Airlines A319-111 Landing In Denver
description:
Welcome on board Frontier Airlines flight 226!

After 2hours and 20minutes in the air, we now descending into the Denver area for our arrival on runway 35L. The flight from Sacramento was a smooth one with some moderate to severe turbulence coming over the Rockies and also on final approach to the runway.

I do want to apologize for the shakiness of the camera during the approach; the ride into Denver was very, very bumpy, but I tried my best to keep it stable, and luckily the camera that I recorded it with is one with a very good image stabilization. 

-- -- --

Video Information -

Aircaft: Airbus A319-111
Airline: Frontier Airlines
Flight #: FFT226
Departure Airport: Sacramento International Airport
Arrival Airport: Denver International Airport
Flight Time (scheduled): 2hours 32minutes
Landing Runway: Runway 35L
Arrival Gate: Gate A33
Camera: Sony DSC-TX7

-- -- --

Thank you for watching this video! Be sure to comment, like, and subscribe! 

The takeoff from Denver, and landing in Cancun will be up soon, so stay tuned!

tags: ['10 лет группе кипелов', 'маргарита пушкина', 'navigator records', 'кипелов', 'терентьев', 'жить вопреки', 'вавилон', 'крокус сити холл', '10 лет', 'я свободен', 'валерий кипелов', 'маврин', 'Дыхание последней любви', 'х лет', 'навигатор рекордс', 'реки времен']
description:

Музыка А. Голованов, В. Кипелов, слова М. Пушкина

1 декабря 2012 года в концертном зале «Крокус Сити Холл» группа «Кипелов» отметила свое 10-летие со своими лучшими песнями за десять лет истории группы. В концерте приняли участие приглашенные гости Сергей Маврин и Сергей Терентьев.
За 10 лет в музыкальном мире происходило много перемен - распадались и воссоединялись группы, менялась мода и мироощущение людей. Но группа «Кипелов» по-прежнему флагман отечественной тяжелой музыки. И конкурентов пока не наблюдается.
Среди наград коллектива за 10 лет такие, как премия MTV Россия в номинации «Лучшая рок-группа» (2004), премия российской музыкальной индустрии «Рекордъ-2007» за лучший живой концерт и даже премия RAMP в номинации «Отцы рока»!
 Фанатам коллектива нет дела до премий, наград и позиций в чатах! Группу «Кипелов» любят не за награды, а за высокий профессионализм, верность себе и предельную самоотдачу во время живых выступлений. Каждый концерт - это особенное, оригинальное шоу, и даже сложно представить, насколько грандиозен размах юбилейного концерта в Москве! Но это не главное.
Главное - это музыка и у вас есть возможность прикоснуться к этой музыке, к этим хитам!

title: Mugen: The Legendary Cell vs The Incredible Hulk!
description: Training vigorously on a desolated planet that once was full of life and full of powerful inhabitants, SPC continued training intensely, becoming more and more powerful with each passing week. After having defeated Wonder Woman, Superman, Namor, The Thing and Thor, SPC marveled at the strength and skill of some of these warriors who despite his egotistical and conceded personality, had earned his respect. Even though SPC knew that he could have continued his destruction on planet Earth and wipe out hundreds of Earth's heroes without rest, SPC heard rumors of two beings with incalculable strength, immense durability and monestrous endurance. Deciding that he had enough playtime on planet Earth...for now, SPC flew out to space and decided to stop and rest on a planet X-xentron, where he would train for his encounter with these beings known as Hulk and Juggernaut. Now after 4 weeks of non-stop intensive training, SPC flew back to Earth were Earth's heros were busy preparing for SPC's return while keeping the people of Earth calm by giving them false news about SPC being defeated. Having located and learned info on Bruce Banner also known as the Incredible Hulk, SPC decided to pick Bruce up and throw him miles into the ocean while he waited for Bruce's transformation to occur as he patiently waited on the San Francisco bridge. Hearing a rumble, SPC looks up to see Hulk land on the bridge where their awesome fight begins.

It's second episode "Gran Dillama" of cartoons "Caminandes" was produced by Pablo Vazquez, Beorn Leonard and Francesco Siddi at the Blender Institute in Amsterdam, the Netherlands. The music is from Jan Morgenstern.

The first episode of cartoons "Caminandes" is available on the following link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gA4_2i8jNrM

Both episodes of the cartoons "Caminandes" has received great appreciation online and it has been selected for screening by many animation festivals.

The funny cartoons are nice to watch for children of 3-12 years old.

“Caminandes” is short for “camino/caminar” (Spanish for path/walk) and Andes - the longest continental mountain range in the world, usually referred as the ‘spine of South America’. The southernmost region of the Americas is called Patagonia, where Pablo is from.

tags: ['po polsku', 'zabawka', 'zabawki', 'toys', 'recenzja', 'review', 'kids toys', 'omówienie', 'dla dzieci', 'dziewczynek', 'bajki', 'girls', 'cartoons', 'edukacyjna', 'education', 'reklama', 'commercial', 'commercials', 'werbung', 'spot', 'television', 'Prinzessin Courtney', 'mit Mikrofon', 'Barbie (Collection Category)', 'Barbie Rock `n Royals', 'Barbie Rockowa Księżniczka', 'Singing Courtney', 'śpiewająca Courtney', 'princess Courtney', 'de', 'niemiecka', 'CMR83', 'doll', 'dolls', 'lalka', 'lalki', 'Puppe', 'Puppen', 'microphone', 'Eine Prinzessin im Rockstar-Camp', 'film', 'movie']
description:
Szczegóły na stronie: http://www.kocham-zabawki.pl

Lalka Courtney inspirowana jest nowym filmem Barbie "Rockowa Księżniczka".
W filmie zderzają się ze sobą dwa różne światy, gdy przez pomyłkę księżniczka i gwiazda pop jadą na ten sam obóz. Podczas pojedynku muzycznego, obie dziewczyny akceptują swoje różnice, odnajdują prawdziwe głosy i uczą się, że razem wszystko jest możliwe.
Dziewczynki pokochają zabawę śpiewającą lalką Courtney, która
magicznie zmienia się z księżniczki w piosenkarkę rockową!
Unieś mikrofon w kierunku ust lalki, żeby aktywować fantastyczną zmianę wyglądu i usłyszeć dwie piosenki znane z filmu „Rockowa Księżniczka”. Sukienka lalki Courtney skręca się, zmieniając ją w gwiazdę muzyki pop podczas śpiewania piosenki (po angielsku). Jako księżniczka nosi ona różową suknię balową ze srebrnym i różowym stanem oraz modną baskinkę Chevron-prin. Jako gwiazda pop jest ubrana w świecący srebrny stan, krótką czarno-różową spódniczkę (z przodu), srebrną baskinkę i długą różową spódnicę (z tyłu). Srebrna tiara i pasujące buty to akcesoria, które zachwycą każdego. Dziewczynki pokochają zmieniać lalkę Courtney z księżniczki w piosenkarkę pop i odwrotnie, tak samo jak zmieniają się ich historie!

Zbierz wszystkie lalki z filmu i stwórz cały zespół, aby zyskać jeszcze więcej możliwości zabawy! Pozostałe lalki sprzedawane oddzielnie. W zestawie lalka Courtney, buty, tiara oraz mikrofon. Lalka nie stoi samodzielnie.

Zabawka przeznaczona dla dzieci od 3 roku życia.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

In Barbie in Rock 'N Royals, two very different worlds collide when a mix-up sends a princess and a pop star to the wrong camps. As they face an epic sing-off, both girls embrace their differences, find their true voices and learn that anything is possible when they work together! Girls will love celebrating the story with this singing Courtney doll, who magically transforms from royal to rocker. Simply lift the pink microphone to her mouth to activate a dramatic fashion transformation and play two songs clips from the film! Courtney doll's skirt twists around, changing her into a trendy pop star while the songs play. As a princess, she wears a pink ball gown with a studded silver and pink bodice and trendy chevron-print peplum. As a pop star, she shines in a studded silver bodice and high-low skirt with black and pink graphic print, silver peplum and sparkly pink skirt. A silvery tiara and matching shoes are show-stopping accessories. Girls will love transforming Courtney doll from princess to pop star and back again as their stories transform, too! Collect her co-stars for a full band and even more possibilities for play (sold separately)! Includes Courtney doll with transforming and musical features, shoes, tiara and microphone (non-removable). Doll cannot stand alone.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

Zwei völlig verschiedene Welten prallen aufeinander, als in dem Film Barbie "Eine Prinzessin im Rockstar-Camp" eine Verwechslung dazu führt, dass eine Prinzessin und ein Rockstar jeweils im falschen Camp landen. Während die beiden Mädchen sich einem großen Gesangswettbewerb stellen, lernen sie ihre unterschiedlichen Fähigkeiten schätzen, finden zu ihren wahren Stimmen und erkennen, dass ihnen gemeinsam alle Möglichkeiten offenstehen! Mit dieser singenden Courtney-Puppe, die sich auf magische Weise von einer Prinzessin in einen Rockstar und wieder zurück verwandelt, werden Mädchen begeistert Filmszenen nachspielen oder sich neue Geschichten ausdenken. Es genügt, sie das Mikrofon zu ihrem Mund heben zu lassen, damit zwei Songs aus dem Film gespielt werden, während ihr Rock sich dreht, und ein trendy Rockstar Outfit zum Vorschein bringt. Als Prinzessin trägt Courtney ein rosafarbenes Ballkleid mit einem reich verzierten Oberteil in Rosa und Silber sowie einem modischen Überröckchen. Als Rockstar glänzt sie in einem mit Schmucksteinen besetzten silberfarbenen Oberteil und einem Rock, der vorn kurz und Pink-Schwarz gemustert und hinten lang und glitzernd Pink ist, sowie von einem silberfarbenen Überröckchen geziert wird. Das silberfarbene Diadem und die passenden Schuhe machen den Look perfekt. Mit weiteren den Stars aus dem Film nachempfundenen Puppen (separat erhältlich) entsteht eine komplette Band, und es eröffnen sich noch mehr tolle Spielmöglichkeiten. Courtney-Puppe mit Verwandlungs- und Musikfunktion, Schuhen, Diadem und Mikrofon (nicht abnehmbar) enthalten.

title: How to make flannel baby blankets
description:
EDIT: Thanks to people being unable to read annotations or something I'm disabling comments due to all the folks who leave stupid remarks about the cats. I'm tired of deleting them. Hope you like the video, if not, go eat a hairball.

I'd just like to emphasize that I DID NOT MAKE THIS VIDEO. MY AUNT DID. I AM JUST POSTING IT FOR HER (WITH HER PERMISSION). 

That being said, in an effort to slow the tide of humorless comments, a few things should be noted:

This video has been getting a lot of comments from people concerned about the presence of allergens from the cats that might be harmful to the babies for which the blankets were made. These people should be relieved to know that 1) they do not need cats present in order to make the blankets themselves, and 2) the blankets were laundered before being given away. And probably laundered AGAIN by the parents before being brought into proximity with their baby. So you may stop filling the comments with your worries and (if I must say) rather unrealistic requests that the video be remade, sans cats.

Cats are everywhere. And they know where you live. Be kind to them.

Or else.

----

My aunt Rachel made this video three years ago and wanted me to post it on my account because she is too lazy to get her own YouTube account. She has trouble with the thought of remembering yet another username and password.

So here you have her video of how to make flannel baby blankets using two pieces of flannel. One piece should be 1.5 yards and the other should be 1 yard. This is for 44/45" fabric (standard size). It takes about an hour to make one start to finish, and an hour and a half to make two. You don't have to wash the fabric ahead of time, in fact it's better not to, and then just wash the blanket once it is done.

Warning: contains cats.

title: Springsteen live in Paris, The wrecking ball tour 2012
description:
2012-07-04 - PALAIS OMNISPORTS DE PARIS-BERCY, PARIS, FRANCE

Soundcheck: EASY MONEY / 4TH OF JULY, ASBURY PARK (SANDY) / WRECKING BALL

WE TAKE CARE OF OUR OWN / WRECKING BALL / BADLANDS / DEATH TO MY HOMETOWN / MY CITY OF RUINS / SPIRIT IN THE NIGHT / THE E STREET SHUFFLE / 4TH OF JULY, ASBURY PARK (SANDY) / JACK OF ALL TRADES / BECAUSE THE NIGHT / DARKNESS ON THE EDGE OF TOWN / JOHNNY 99 / DARLINGTON COUNTY / EASY MONEY / WAITIN' ON A SUNNY DAY / THE PROMISED LAND / THE WAY YOU DO THE THINGS YOU DO - 634-5789 (SOULSVILLE, U.S.A.) / INDEPENDENCE DAY / THE RIVER / THE RISING / OUT IN THE STREET / LAND OF HOPE AND DREAMS - PEOPLE GET READY / WE ARE ALIVE / BORN IN THE U.S.A. / BORN TO RUN / BOBBY JEAN / DANCING IN THE DARK / TENTH AVENUE FREEZE-OUT / AMERICAN LAND

The first of two nights at Bercy and the twelfth time Springsteen has played the arena. Back to the stage after a ten-day break and Bruce plays no less than three July 4 specials - "4th Of July, Asbury Park (Sandy)", "Darlington County" and a solo piano "Independence Day". In addition "American Land" closes the show. "La Vie en rose" (best known as the signature song of Edith Piaf) welcomes the band on stage, played by the accordion duo of Roy and Charlie. Patti returns to the stage for the first time since Los Angeles - as a result "Easy Money" makes a reappearance, replacing "Shackled And Drawn".

Grand Theft Auto V is an open world, action-adventure video game developed by Rockstar North and published by Rockstar Games. It was released on 17 September 2013 for the PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 consoles. It is the fifteenth title in the Grand Theft Auto series, and the first main entry since Grand Theft Auto IV was released in 2008. As one of the last titles to release exclusively during the seventh generation of video game consoles, Grand Theft Auto V was highly anticipated preceding its release.

Grand Theft Auto V is played in third-person and combines driving and action gameplay in an open world environment, allowing the player to interact with the game world at their leisure. The game is set within the fictional state of San Andreas, which is based on Southern California, affording the player free roam over the world's countryside and the fictional city of Los Santos, which is based on Los Angeles. The single-player story is told through three player-controlled protagonists whom the player switches between—Michael, Trevor and Franklin—and the story follows their efforts to plan and execute six large heists to accrue wealth for themselves. An online multiplayer mode is included, allowing up to sixteen players to engage in both co-operative and competitive gameplay in a recreation of the single-player setting.

title: Lifting up a lady.mp4
description:
On the 20/06/2010 at about 11:05 train no 988562 travelling from Pretoria to Cullinan hauling 417 tonnages for 48 axles using a steam locomotives came to stop between  KM/P 8 and 9 because of derailment of locomotive no 3117. the coal wagon ,water tank no 30025753 and a passenger coach no 40092 which was behind the water tank because of loosen rails and stolen wooden sleepers
The incident happened at a down gradient just inside the Warning board of Cullinan station at the curve in the short cutting 
The locomotive ,the tender and the coal wagon  were lying on the side , the water tank wheel were hanging on the air and the passenger coach derailed with all four wheels 
The passenger was removed from the train and no injuries reported and walked to the station . The train personnel were also not injured

title: TU12 In Certification! @4JStudios Confirmed! Change List Released!
tags: ['Minecraft', 'Minecraft Xbox', 'Minecraft Xbox 360', 'Minecraft (Xbox 360)', 'Minecraft (Xbox 360) Edition', 'TU12 Release Date', 'TU12', 'TU12 In Certification', 'Minecraft (Xbox 360) TU12 Release Date', 'Minecraft (Xbox 360) TU12 In Certification', 'Eskimo', 'xXxIncisionxXx', '4JStudios', '4J Studios', 'Change List', 'TU12 Change List', 'Released', 'TheChaoticCreeper', 'BigBSt4tz2', 'TheGamingLemon', 'Stampylonghead', 'iBallisticSquid', 'TU12 Seed Showcase', 'Seed Showcase', 'Minecraft (Xbox 360) Seed Showcase']
description:
Let's break 300 LIKES for TU12 FINALLY being in certification! 

Full Change List: 
http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/1274802-mcxbla-title-update-change-logs-title-update-12/

"Minecraft Xbox 360 TU12 Full Change List"

New Mobs

- Ocelot/Cat
- Iron Golem
- Baby Villager

New Items

- Redstone Lamp
- Jungle Wood Stairs
- Jungle Wood Half Slab
- Jungle Wood Block
- Jungle Wood Planks
- Jungle Tree Sapling
- Ocelot Spawn Egg
- (Creative Mode only) Chiseled Stone Brick
- (Creative Mode only) Mob Heads (Skeleton, Wither Skeleton, Zombie, Human and Creeper)

Changes/Additions

- New Tutorial World.
- New map height limit (256 instead of 128).
- Jungle Biome
- Jungle trees
- Cocoa beans grow on Jungle trees
- Slabs and Stairs can be placed upside-down by placing them below a block.
- Added Corner Stairs and upside down Corner Stairs.
- Added 3D dropped items.
- Added dispensing Boats and Minecarts to Dispenser.
- New ambient cave sounds.
- New AI for Mobs.
- Added rare drops for Mobs.
- Villagers will have children if there is room in their village.
- Zombie sieges will occur occasionally at night.
- Zombies break down doors on Hard Mode.
- Crafting recipe for ladder now yields 3 ladders instead of 2.
- Placing blocks on grass will replace it.
- Lava now has a faint rumbling sound effect, and large particles that hop out of the lava produce a popping sound.
- Very rare Desert Wells can be found in Desert biomes.
- Increased max boats in a world to 40.
- When in the Nether, Snow Golems will melt and die same as when they are in Desert biomes.
- Abandoned Mineshafts can generate with wooden bridges now when generated over a cave or over top another tunnel.
- Doors have been updated so that double doors work better with Redstone.
- Added a Favorites tab to the Skin Selector menu, storing most recently used skins.
- Added support for Texture Packs and Mash-up Packs, and display of these in the Minecraft Store.

Fixes

- Fixed local player shadows not being displayed.
- Fixed a few issues with the Privileges settings.
- Fixed visible seams in clouds.
- Fixed 3rd person camera issues with water, where the underwater filter would be randomly removed.
- Fix for structures generating at the edge of a world.
- Fix for putting enchanted items in a Minecart With Chest and destroying it removes the enchantments.
- Fix for breaking a bow having improper animation.
- Fix to make Minecarts run at the correct speed.
- Fixed a few memory leaks.
- Fixed issue with "Can Open Containers" option.
- Fixed issues with "Can Build and Mine" option.
- Fixed Issue with TNT blocks being triggered by explosions even with "TNT explodes" option off.
- Fixed Wolves not tilting their heads when the player has a bone in their hand.
- Fixed the color of Potion particles status effect to match the Potion color.
- Fix for doors spitting in half and glitching in open/closed motion when mined.
- Fixed artifacts on edge of flames when in first person.
- Fixed a lot of game lighting issues.

description:
The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim review. Classic Game Room presents a CGR Undertow review of The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim for Xbox 360 developed by Bethesda Game Studios and published by Bethesda Softworks.

The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim is here to take a stand and let the gaming world know that amazing single-player experiences are still here and very-much alive. Throughout Skyrim's entirety, developer Bethesda has really found a harmony of design choices that all coalesce into a single, united identity of gameplay, art and execution. Simply put: The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim is one of the greatest adventure role-playing games ever created. You shouldn't miss it.

This video review features video gameplay footage of The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim for Xbox 360 and audio commentary from Classic Game Room's Steve.

title: Draining Fuel from the Wrecked 1995 Ford Crown Victoria
description:
While getting ready to mow the lawn, I noticed that not only was the mower out of fuel, but my fuel container was also empty. Here, I fill up the fuel container using the leftover fuel in the wrecked 1995 Ford Crown Victoria.

Not having the fuel pump relay, PCM, and associated wiring, I wired the fuel pump directly to a booster battery for the power source. Then, I ran a piece of 5/8" heater hose from the fuel supply line that normally goes to the engine into the fuel container. The filling process took about seven minutes. (9/7/2013)

title: Angelica - Thrive EPK (Official)
tags: ['angelica', 'the murde of my sweet', 'frontiers records', 'aor', 'hard rock', 'daniel flores', 'Thrive', 'Magnus Karlsson', 'primal fear', 'Jesper Stromblad', 'in flames', 'Per Berquist', 'Matt Guillory (Record Producer)']
description:
Don't forget to LIKE the Frontiers Records Facebook page https://www.facebook.com/frontiersrecordsofficial

Frontiers Records is excited to present the world the talents of Swedish singer ANGELICA with the release of her debut album "Thrive" on November 29th in Europe and December 3rd in North America. 
 
Best known for being the singer in The Murder of My Sweet, Angelica Rylin finally decided to pursue her childhood dream and to walk in the footsteps of such amazing singers such as Ann Wilson of Heart, Leigh Matty of Romeo's Daughter or Robin Beck and record her debut solo album in a true Melodic Rock style. 

Some Melodic Rock songwriting luminaries answered the call in order to create the magic harmonies and music displayed on Angelica's debut album. "Harry Hess, Daniel Flores, Robert Sall, Alessandro Del Vecchio and Anders Wigelius all contributed", says Angelica and some excellent guitarists such as Jesper Stromblad (In Flames), Magnus Karlsson (Primal Fear), Per Berquist (Smash Into Pieces) also appear on the album. There is also a very special performance by keyboardist Matt Guillory (James LaBrie). Still Angelica wrote or co-wrote several songs on her record, showing another side of her abilities.

"I got the chance to step out of my comfort zone and just focus on being a great singer. I also got to do a couple of amazing co-writes, for instance with Harry Hess of Harem Scarem" continues Angelica "but what I'm most happy about is that I got to include a couple of my own songs too. It's a great mix of classic but modern AOR love songs".

Helped by producer, drummer and songwriting partner Daniel Flores (FIND ME, SEVENTH WONDER; THE MURDER OF MY SWEET), Angelica managed to create a superb album which offers soaring and instantly likeable hook lines, solid guitar riffs and a crisp sound. "After releasing two albums with The Murder of My Sweet I get an opportunity to show my fans a slightly different side of me and at the same time have fun and explore another side of rock music that I grew up with and truly love" tells Angelica. "I have pushed my boundaries vocally on this album and grown as a singer, which is very important for me on a more personal level. I guess this is every singer's dream!"

 "Thrive" final track listing includes: Breaking My Heart; I Am Strong; To Your Rescue; Can't Stop Love; Nothing Else You Can Break; Riding Out The Storm; Rain On My Parade; Losers In Paradise; You Will Never Win; This Kiss Is Just For You; I'm Not Waiting; Take Me To Your Heart. Breaking My Heart (bonus videoclip)

Enjoy the YouTube trailer presentation: http://youtu.be/1EZ2pOL5yFk and listen to the streaming of the single "Breaking My Heart" on the Frontiers Records webradio: www.frontiers.it/webradio

title: How To Make Steel Targets:  Cheap & Easy!
tags: ['IntoWeapons', 'how to', 'make', 'best', 'easy', 'cheap', 'budget', 'steel', 'targets', 'shooting', 'swinging', 'hanging', 'steel targets', 'gun range', 'target practice', 'how to make', 'how to make steel targets', 'making steel targets', 'diy', 'diy steel targets', 'homemade', 'cheap steel target', 'metal targets', 'metal', 'shooting targets', 'build', 'make your own', 'diy targets', 'pistol', 'rifle', 'AR500', 'plates', 'steel plate', 'handgun', 'auto', 'reset', 'universal', 'calibers', 'all', 'safe', 'best steel target', 'mild', 'body armor', 'gun target', 'for shooting', 'cheapest', '9mm', '.22']
description:
How to easily and cheaply make DIY Steel Targets that hang and swing.  These homemade steel targets are made out of scrap steel plates (from scrapyard) or purchased hardened steel target plates, along with some common Shepherd's Hook's for outdoor gardening.  With a fresh coat of spray paint or a new adhesive paper target applied between uses, they are like new every time!  See below for more on this project and quick links to all materials needed!

**BEST Spinning Steel Targets with Auto Reset!:  http://amzn.to/2Etj43o

**AR500 10-in Steel Gong Target for all Calibers!:  http://amzn.to/2E0V0Hw

**Shepherds Hook's for Hanging Targets:  http://amzn.to/2GAVm68

**100-pack Adhesive Reactive 8-in. Splatter Targets:  http://amzn.to/2E44d1y

These homemade steel targets are a decent alternative to purchasing hanging steel or spinning targets, but nearly every variation of swinging or spinning steel target is available online for reasonable prices.  I use a readily available Shepherd's Hook to hang the steel plates.  Local salvage or recycling yards are the best place to get the steel and they usually are happy to sell it to you by the pound.  If you are nice they will even punch a hole in it for you with a propane torch.  You can also purchase Hardened Steel Target Plates (like AR500) with pre-cut holes for hanging in any (safe) fashion you wish.

If you want to take the steel targets a step further, it is nice to have some self-adhesive reactive paper targets on-hand to attach.  You can stick them to the face of the steel target for easy shot identification.


**Swinging Metal Target Systems:  http://amzn.to/2Etj43o
**AR500 Hardened Steel Hanging Targets:  http://amzn.to/2E0V0Hw
**Shepherds Hook's for Hanging Targets:  http://amzn.to/2GAVm68
**Adhesive Reactive 8-in. Splatter Targets:  http://amzn.to/2E44d1y

title: [HD] 산속의 KTX-산천 / 山中のKTX-山川 / KTX-Sancheon in the mountains
tags: ['코레일', 'KORAIL', '영동선', '嶺東線', 'Yeongdong Line', '심포리역', '深浦里駅', 'Simpori Station', '통리역', '桶里駅', 'Tongri Station', '갑종회송', '甲種回送', 'KTX-산천', 'KTX-山川', 'KTX-Sancheon', '7402열차', 'South Korea', 'GH2']
description:
2012년 6월 1일, 강릉역에서 원주-강릉간 복선전철 기공식이 있었습니다.

그 때에 배경으로서 KTX-산천 24편성이 동원되었었으며, 6월 3일 다시 서울로 돌아왔습니다. 견인은 KTX 구원전용 기관차인 7574호가 담당하였습니다.

본 영상은 6월 3일, 서울로 돌아가기 위해 KTX-산천이 스위치백을 지나, 영동선 심포리역과 통리역을 통과하는 모습입니다. 이 모습을 촬영하기 위해 전국에서 많은 철도동호인들이 이 열차가 운행하는 영동선, 태백선, 충북선 주변에 집결, 촬영하였었습니다.

2012年6月1日韓国の江原道の江陵駅で原州-江陵間複線電鉄の鍬入れ式(起工式)がありました。
大統領や長官も列席する大した式だったんですので、その背景でKTX-山川が動員されました。ソウルから江陵まで往復の甲種回送はKTX救援専用の機関車7574号が担当しますし、KTX-山川は6月3日ソウルへ帰りました。

この動画はKTX-山川が嶺東線の深浦里駅と桶里駅を通過する風景です。
この風景を撮るために全国でたくさんの鉄ファンたちがこのスイッチバックの周りに集結しました。

1st June 2012, groundbreaking ceremony at Gangneung Station for new electric-double track railroad between Wonju and Gangneung.
KTX-Sancheon was returned to Seoul on 3rd June, running in the mountains leaded by Diesel Locomotive.

Colina Vainilla 3:
Nada más comenzar la fase, ve a la derecha donde vas a una plataforma formada por calaveras. Sube a ella y ve a la derecha del todo hasta que llegues a una tubería. Pégate a ella y salta para descubrir un bloque secreto en el que te tienes que apoyar para avanzar. Luego tienes que seguir yendo hacia la derecha por el único camino posible, hasta que llegas a la meta que te hace completar la fase.

Colina Vainilla 4:
Lo único que tienes que hacer es llegar a la derecha del todo, pero es un poco complicado, ya que de vez en cuando aparecen unas balas de cañón que van hacia ti. Además hay zonas en las que tienes que saltar por las ramas para poder avanzar.

CLIP DESCRIPTION:
Dressed in disguise, Rostov (Richard Lynch) pretends to welcome a boat of refugees while really interested in the goods below deck.

FILM DESCRIPTION:
This red-baiting action film stars Chuck Norris as Matt Hunter, a retired CIA agent who lives in the Florida Everglades. A communist invasion of Miami brings Hunter out of retirement to fight the encroaching hordes led by everyone's favorite low-budget bad guy, Richard Lynch. The film is extremely jingoistic, presenting the evil communists staging an invasion on Christmas, demolishing a church, and attempting to blow up a school bus full of children. From the same school of thinking which produced Rambo and Red Dawn, this film at least features some convincing gore by makeup wizard Tom Savini (Friday the 13th), working on his third gig for director Joseph Zito. Zito and Savini returned with Red Scorpion.

title: Eco_Drop Shower
description:
Saving water has become one of the most important habits of a modern day human being.
We all know that for most people self-regulation is very difficult.
So a little help comes from the Eco_Drop Shower.
It looks like a normal shower but it is not.
The secret is in the base: normally it is wonderfully shaped with concentric circles conveying the waves of the falling drops.
But after having been staying under the water for too long something happens.. those circles rise, so that you are not allowed to stay longer in the shower, and you are forced to turn off the water and go out.
"Eco_Drop" Shower will help save water and energy.

title: Johan Tronestam - Discovering the Unknown Space
description:
Johan Tronestam is from Sweden. His father is a musician and therefore there were many music instruments in his parental home. His father wanted him to become a violin player, but Johan's favorite instrument was the electric organ. 
When he heard "Oxygene" from Jean Michel Jarre for the first time something happened inside him. Johan says : "New doors opened for me and I knew that I had to have synthesizers. But synthesizers were very expensive instruments. The price of my favorite synth Korg Trident was 28 000 Swedish Krones back in 1982. I was a student and I didn´t have that money,  so the music store became my second home. I remember the moment when I finally could afford the Korg, and when I had the equipment at home I was so lucky!"
  
Johan played in various music groups. In the 90s he started composing his own instrumental synth music. The music is created in his own studio. His music is very personal. He is influenced by Vangelis, JM Jarre, Mike Oldfield, Tangerine Dream, Tim Blake, Neuronium, Kraftwerk, Klaus Schulze and similar artists.

His first big project was called " A journey under the stars" ( 2004 )
His first pressed album was "The Island"( 2008 ): The music was inspired by Johan's  experiences on the island of Åland. The mysticism, movement and attractive nature appealed to him enormously.
"The long journey" was composed in 2009.This project reflects a future where men has found a possibility to travel to other stars. But not without mistakes...
"The long journey" was influenced by the astronomer/philosopher/author Peter Nilsons (1937-1998). And also by Harry Martinsons space poem "Anaria".
"Planet X" (2010)
This album reflects a future where men has been contacted by extraterrestrials. Planet X is based on the possibility of life in other worlds.
"Stories from the dawn" (2011)
An exciting album that challenges different styles of music but still with the frame in the electronic music area. This album concerns our ancient history and its awakening
"Far away" ( 2012 )
This album is partly inspired by Arthur C. Clarke's 2010. The idea of how the extraterrestrial super-intelligence is traveling at the speed of thought. Being able to move around and admire the endless universal fireworks. 
At the moment Johan is working on an album called "Roots from the North", a project linked to Nordic roots and legends. Both in North America, Northern Europe and the top of Asia. 
"Discovering the Unknown Space" is from his outstanding album 'Far Away". (2012 )

INFO UTILI SULLA PESCA A SURF CASTING:
Il Surfcasting è una modalità di pesca sportiva che si effettua dalla spiaggia, con robuste canne, capaci di lanciare il complesso terminale a distanze considerevoli dalla riva. a disciplina del surfcasting nella sua origine oceanica sfrutta l'andamento delle maree, le quali possono produrre, nel loro alternarsi, significative turbolenze sottomarine nei pressi della costa. Tali turbolenze, sommovendo il fondale sabbioso con moto circolare, creano una zona particolarmente ricca di cibo, dai microorganismi ad animali di taglia maggiore (anellidi e granchi), i quali sono base dell'alimentazione per i pesci 'grufolatori' e 'predatori', grandi e piccoli. Una vera e propria catena alimentare.
Nella versione mediterranea del surfcasting, le maree non sono sufficienti da sole a produrre tale turbolenza: per questo ci si avvale dell'ausilio delle mareggiate. Osservando il mare aperto in presenza di moto ondoso di intensità apprezzabile, si noterà come le onde inizino a "gonfiarsi" tutte nello stesso punto.
Quando la metà dell'altezza dell'onda è maggiore della profondità del mare, quello è il punto in cui inizia il vomere delle onde sul fondo e quindi, il deposito organico tipico del surfcasting. I grossi predatori, meta ambita più d'ogni altra in questa specialità, si avventurano tra quei flutti, in cerca del cibo, costituito dagli organismi dissepolti o dai pesci-esca in pascolo sul settore.

title: VDOT: Interstate 81 In-Place Pavement Recycling
description:
Using three pavement recycling processes together on a single rehabilitation project on the U.S. interstate system had never been done -- until Virginia did it in 2011. 

VDOT employed full-depth reclamation, cold central-plant recycling and cold in-place recycling to rebuild a 3.7-mile, two-lane section of southbound Interstate 81 near Staunton.

The agency reduced its estimated construction time by two-thirds and saved millions of dollars by using the three pavement recycling methods to reconstruct this part of the interstate.
